title: Former Walker donor Stan Hubbard gives to Jeb Bush after giving to rivals
text: Stanley Hubbard, a major financial backer of Scott Walker before his campaign for president fizzled, recently made the maximum allowable contribution to Jeb Bush's campaign, making Bush the fifth Republican candidate the Minnesota media mogul has given to after Walker's downward spiral began.
